<STRONG></STRONG>&nbsp;If you’ve recently introduced a product that has raised the standard of consumer electronics innovation, chances are it deserves an Innovations 2008 Design and Engineering Award. <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/attendees/awards/innovations/rd_entries.asp">Enter today</A>.&nbsp;<BR><BR><STRONG< SPAN></STRONG><STRONG>Entries must qualify for each of the following criteria:</STRONG><BR>
