<STRONG>Entrants agree to these rules:</STRONG><BR>
<UL>
<LI>Products entered must fit within one of the official award categories. </LI>
<LI>Products entered must be available for sale&nbsp;to the public at U. S. retail outlets or on the Internet between March 1, 2007,&nbsp;and February 29, 2008. </LI>
