<LI>All entries must be submitted&nbsp;via the online submission process. E-mailed and hard-copy entries will no longer be accepted.&nbsp; </LI>
<LI><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Two product photographs must accompany and are required for each entry. The photos must be two DIFFERENT views of the product.<BR></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ">
