<LI>E-mailed and/or hard copy submission forms are no longer accepted. </LI></OL><BR><STRONG>Remember</STRONG>:&nbsp; <BR>You must provide a minimum of two different high-resolution photos of your product, with up to five different views of the product. Computer renderings are not acceptable. Images must be submitted in an&nbsp;EPS format. All photos must be submitted via the online submission process. E-mailed and hard copy photos will no longer be accepted.
